_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
Packy here with a quick one. Eight Sleep announced its Pod 4 Ultra this wee=
k, and as a very happy Eight Sleep customer (but sadly, not investor), I=E2=
=80=99m excited. I have a lot of redeeming qualities, but sleep isn=E2=80=
=99t one of them. I snore. I wake up in the middle of the night. And when I=
 do, I get tired and noticeably less energetic and creative.=20
This mattress detects snoring and adjusts automatically to stop it. If it w=
orks, I can=E2=80=99t imagine a higher-ROI investment. Do you know how many=
 thousands and thousands of words I could write if I just slept a little bi=
t better? We=E2=80=99re about to find out.=20
We=E2=80=99ll be back in your inbox on Tuesday.
